  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421880/extras/74bfe1ef1bc78b606ca15be859beb753.avif?t=1741612101\" width=576 height=360 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421880/extras/bc8270ef09cca6ec94c647ad4237e5fc.avif?t=1741612101\" width=576 height=372 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BIRDS. EVERYWHERE. AND THEY’RE IN YOUR HEAD!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're out-numbered, out-flapped, and totally ticked off! And these pesky vermin are using MIND TRICKS to throw you off!  But lucky you - a not so <i>close, close </i>friend lent you a ROCKET SHIP! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ignore distractions, blast those squawkers, and show ‘em WHO’S BOSS!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421880/extras/ae3552c477f61aa9296a469e4a72b1c8.avif?t=1741612101\" width=576 height=360 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421880/extras/d9b10314d76bd197d6bc30dae8d3a479.avif?t=1741612101\" width=576 height=372 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MAJOR RICHARD JOHNSON - SOLDIER OF FORTUNE TURNED MASTER BUILDER!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At <strong>RETROA RETROA</strong>, the agency so good they named it twice, he crafts high-stakes training simulations. But he’s drowning in unfinished levels! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Your mission?</strong> Jump in, test his wild creations, and help him clear the backlog! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Time to BUILD. Time to CONQUER. Be a RETROA RETROA BUILDA!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421880/extras/105d742b61d8388b8e8b200884e1c1a0.avif?t=1741612101\" width=576 height=360 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421880/extras/ab46d2053ab12fdf79e630f16456523e.avif?t=1741612101\" width=576 height=372 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>THE SLIMES TRUST YOU… BUT THEY CAN NEVER KNOW.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They’re trapped, desperate to escape, they dream of freedom. - but the dungeon level's never end. They must NEVER know. Drop blocks, guide them upward, and <strong>never</strong> let them lose hope! The more lives you have, the harder it gets. One left? Easy… until one mistake <strong>seals their fate!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Help them climb. Help them believe. Even if they’ll never leave.</strong> </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421880/extras/74bfe1ef1bc78b606ca15be859beb753.avif?t=1741612101\" width=576 height=360 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421880/extras/bc8270ef09cca6ec94c647ad4237e5fc.avif?t=1741612101\" width=576 height=372 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BIRDS. EVERYWHERE. AND THEY’RE IN YOUR HEAD!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're out-numbered, out-flapped, and totally ticked off! And these pesky vermin are using MIND TRICKS to throw you off!  But lucky you - a not so <i>close, close </i>friend lent you a ROCKET SHIP! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ignore distractions, blast those squawkers, and show ‘em WHO’S BOSS!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421880/extras/ae3552c477f61aa9296a469e4a72b1c8.avif?t=1741612101\" width=576 height=360 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421880/extras/d9b10314d76bd197d6bc30dae8d3a479.avif?t=1741612101\" width=576 height=372 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MAJOR RICHARD JOHNSON - SOLDIER OF FORTUNE TURNED MASTER BUILDER!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At <strong>RETROA RETROA</strong>, the agency so good they named it twice, he crafts high-stakes training simulations. But he’s drowning in unfinished levels! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Your mission?</strong> Jump in, test his wild creations, and help him clear the backlog! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Time to BUILD. Time to CONQUER. Be a RETROA RETROA BUILDA!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421880/extras/105d742b61d8388b8e8b200884e1c1a0.avif?t=1741612101\" width=576 height=360 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421880/extras/ab46d2053ab12fdf79e630f16456523e.avif?t=1741612101\" width=576 height=372 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>THE SLIMES TRUST YOU… BUT THEY CAN NEVER KNOW.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They’re trapped, desperate to escape, they dream of freedom. - but the dungeon level's never end. They must NEVER know. Drop blocks, guide them upward, and <strong>never</strong> let them lose hope! The more lives you have, the harder it gets. One left? Easy… until one mistake <strong>seals their fate!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Help them climb. Help them believe. Even if they’ll never leave.</strong> </p>",
